    <item>
      <title>巴斯说，中国需要一个强大的人民币来购买美国商品。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-10/china-needs-a-strong-yuan-to-buy-us-goods-bass-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Hayman Capital的创始人兼首席信息官Kyle Bass在“彭博公开兴趣”上说，中国的经济与美国的“不同地方”与美国的“不同地方”，它需要强大的人民币才能以美元购买商品。贝斯还谈到了中国对美国的杠杆作用以及人民币的能力较弱。  （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-10/china-needs-a-strong-yuan-to-buy-us-goods-bass-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 14:07:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>POILIEVRE推动城市减少新房屋建设的税收</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/poilievre-to-push-cities-to-cut-taxes-on-new-home-construction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党领导人皮埃尔·波利夫（Pierre Poilievre）宣布了一项计划，促使城市削减加拿大新房屋建筑的发展指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/poilievre-to-push-cities-to-cut-taxes-on-new-home-construction</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 14:02:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储的施密德说，他“完全专注”通货膨胀风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/fed-s-schmid-says-he-s-squarely-focused-on-inflation-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[堪萨斯城的美联储银行总裁杰夫·施密德（Jeff Schmid）表示，如果美国中央银行家被迫平衡其价格稳定目标与其充分就业的授权，他将优先考虑通货膨胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/fed-s-schmid-says-he-s-squarely-focused-on-inflation-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴斯说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-10/china-loses-a-tit-for-tat-trade-war-bass-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Hayman Capital的创始人兼CIO凯尔·巴斯（Kyle Bass）表示，如果中国试图对美国的关税付出巨大的关税，它将输掉。他说，最后，在唐纳德·特朗普总统获得所有贸易协议签署之后，美国将变得更加强大。他处于“彭博公开兴趣”上。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-10/china-loses-a-tit-for-tat-trade-war-bass-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 13:57:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着关税焦虑偏移的静音CPI，美国的信用恐惧增加了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/credit-fear-gauges-worsen-as-tariff-concerns-offset-soft-cpi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当投资者担心关税的经济影响时，对公司信贷违约的担忧升级，尽管美国通货膨胀数据在新征税之前对消费者有所缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/credit-fear-gauges-worsen-as-tariff-concerns-offset-soft-cpi</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 13:05:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英格兰银行在市场破裂后停止出售长期债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/bank-of-england-halts-sale-of-long-dated-debt-after-market-ruptures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英格兰银行暂时停止了在其定量收紧计划下销售长期债券的出售，在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税点燃后，镀金产生的兴起后，屈服于市场压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/bank-of-england-halts-sale-of-long-dated-debt-after-market-ruptures</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 12:20:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>不利于美元债务的贸易战争损失，没有新兴市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/no-emerging-market-is-spared-from-trade-war-losses-on-dollar-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税全面席卷了新兴市场债务，迄今为止，每个国家 /地区都有以君主和企业成果计价的债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/no-emerging-market-is-spared-from-trade-war-losses-on-dollar-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 11:27:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储的鲍曼（Bowman）接受参议院的烧烤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/fed-s-bowman-to-undergo-senate-grilling-over-bank-views</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国美联储州长米歇尔·鲍曼（Michelle Bowman）将于周四在参议院银行委员会听证会上面临审查，因为立法者认为她的提名是监督副主席。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/fed-s-bowman-to-undergo-senate-grilling-over-bank-views</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 10:30:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>即使关税溃败困扰了长期债务，美国国债反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/treasuries-chaos-is-triggering-aftershocks-across-global-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在上个月的美国通货膨胀率意外涨潮之后，较短的期限损失了唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）不断发展的贸易政策，使债券交易者平静下来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/treasuries-chaos-is-triggering-aftershocks-across-global-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 01:43:44 GMT</pubDate>
